categories: Category:Unidentified Jedi of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: An unidentified Jedi lived sometime before the Third battle of Felucia. They somehow died on Felucia.

This unidentified Jedi was only mentioned in the Star Wars: Clone Wars Adventures video game on the collection of "Forgotten Jedi Gear" on Felucia. Their species and gender is not specified. Their equipment would not have been able to survive longer than the Ruusan Reformation, thus they lived after the Reformation.
